()Common Methods & Use:-
Method	                             Description	             Code Example
getApplicationName()--------Account ka application name------link.getApplicationName();
getNativeIdentity()---------System me user ka username-------link.getNativeIdentity();
getEntitlements()-----------Account ke entitlements list-----link.getEntitlements();
getAttributes()-------------Account ke custom attributes-----link.getAttributes();
setApplicationName(String)--Change app name------------------link.setApplicationName("Salesforce");
setNativeIdentity(String)---Change username------------------link.setNativeIdentity("rahul.sf");
addEntitlement(String)------Entitlement add------------------link.addEntitlement("Read");
removeEntitlement(String)---Entitlement remove---------------link.removeEntitlement("Write");
getStatus()-----------------Account status (Active/Inactive)---link.getStatus();

Code Example:-
Link link = user.getLinks().get(0);
System.out.println("App: " + link.getApplicationName());
System.out.println("Username: " + link.getNativeIdentity());
System.out.println("Entitlements: " + link.getEntitlements());

// Add/Remove entitlement
link.addEntitlement("Admin");
link.removeEntitlement("Read");
