🔹 setCorrelationId(String):-
👉 Ye SailPoint aur external system ke beech mapping id set karta hai.
📌 Use case:-
Identity ko correct account se match karna
Reconciliation ke time matching

🔹 getCorrelationId():-
👉 Wo mapping id return karta hai.

🔹 setExternalId(String):-
👉 External system ka real unique id store karta hai.
📌 Example:-
Active Directory GUID
SAP user ID

🔹 getExternalId():-
👉 External system ka id return karta hai.

✅ Code Example (Without * import)
import sailpoint.object.Link;

public class LinkIdExample {

    public static void main(String[] args) {

        Link link = new Link();

        // =========================
        // 🔹 CORRELATION ID
        // =========================

        // setCorrelationId → mapping id set karna
        link.setCorrelationId("CORR-12345");

        // getCorrelationId → mapping id lena
        System.out.println("Correlation ID: " + link.getCorrelationId());


        // =========================
        // 🔹 EXTERNAL ID
        // =========================

        // setExternalId → external system ka id set karna
        link.setExternalId("EXT-98765");

        // getExternalId → external id lena
        System.out.println("External ID: " + link.getExternalId());
    }
}
✅ Output
Correlation ID: CORR-12345
External ID: EXT-98765
